Laptop (how to use)

https://streamable.com/t4u7i7


for moblie users

1.First tap on the folder or mode you want.
2.then tap the option you want.
3.tap the copy button.
4.tap the share button and tap add bookmark.change the name if you want.and save
5.the tap the button that is located on the top left corner of you screen.
6.tap bookmarks and look for the bookmark you just saved.
7.tap edit and tap the bookmark.
8.erase the url and paste in the code,tap enter.
9.go to market and the tap the bookmark,and the cheat will activate.

BUT this only works for the add tokens hack and the code for all games hack.

so the rest is ctrl shift i and paste in the code then hit enter.
